    {
      "name": "Envelope",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>The demon makes an attack against a target, attempting to wrap itself<br>around its prey. If successful, instead of dealing damage the target is Restrained and will begin to&nbsp;suffocate soon. The target can attempt a TN 6 Exertion roll to break free on his turn. The demon can&nbsp;envelope a single target of one size greater than itself, two of equal size, four of one size less, or&nbsp;eight of two sizes less. In cases where the demon has enveloped several targets of various sizes, two&nbsp;Tiny targets count as one Small, two Small count as one Medium, two Medium as one Large, two&nbsp;Large as one Huge, and two Huge count as one Massive.</p>",
        "action": "major"
      },
